[2006-06-16: sasha]
 * Fixed problem with Java windows getting remapped when they are being
   withdrawn. Java tends to change its hints just before unmapping window
   causing AS to do XMapSubwindows on entire frame - which would in turn remap
   client , while it was just unmapped by java. Bunch of idiots

