   and it takes bindings used by Emacs. #Key Meta_L      A       A
   WarpFore #Key Meta_R      A       A       WarpBack
 * Those settings make a more sensible choice for most users who want an
   intuitive AfterStep right out of the box (they will be able to modify this
   config later on if they are not pleased with it): SmartPlacement
   RandomPlacement #NoPPosition

